                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d559">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 838.00/1277.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Chargé <persName type="from">Johnson</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Santo Domingo</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1915-08-28T11:00:00-04:40">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 28, 1915—11 a.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Bobo on Cuban vessel in harbor. At my request pending quick reply to this
                    telegram vessel will be detained here by Cuban Minister and Bobo kept under
                    guard by Dominican Government which is desirous of compelling him to proceed to
                    next port, Santiago de Cuba. Has the Department any request to make of the
                    Dominican Government?</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Johnson</hi>.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
